A 14th-century fort, reimagined with mindful luxury✨ From sunrise yoga to poolside drinks, every detail at @sixsensesfortbarwara felt like a love letter to rest, beauty, and the earth. Sustainability never looked this stunning, felt just like royalty🧘🏽‍♀️🤍💆🏻‍♀️🤌🏼

Staying at @sixsensesfortbarwara was more than just a getaway,
it was a return to stillness, to intention, and to beauty rooted in tradition. Set within a stunningly restored 14th-century fort in Ranthambhore, every stone whispered history, while every corner radiated mindful luxury.

From the moment we arrived, it was clear that this wasn’t your typical hotel stay. The Aravalli Suite stole our hearts with hill views, a private garden, and even an outdoor shower that made mornings feel magical!!

The food was exceptional, from classic Rajasthani flavours like Laal Maas ( I might have had the BEST laal Maas) to nourishing, plant-forward dishes! I also learned how to make my favourite garlic chutney! The staff and their hospitality has my heart! They truly treat you like royalty!👀

What stood out the most was the brand’s commitment to sustainability, locally sourced ingredients, refillable glass bottles, organic amenities, and an overall philosophy of conscious luxury that left a lasting impression! 

Overall, it was a dream vacation and I highly recommend you plan a trip asap!👀
